# .env (never commit this file)

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# LLM Auth — Sidekick uses Copilot API (primary) + GitHub Models (fallback)
# Both use the same GitHub token. Normally auto-detected via `gh auth token`.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Only set this if gh CLI is unavailable:
# GITHUB_TOKEN=<your-github-pat>

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Whisper model override (optional)
# Sidekick uses local Whisper exclusively — no cloud STT, no API keys.
# Default model is small.en. Override to trade size for accuracy:
#   base.en   ~150MB  fastest, ~8-10% WER
#   small.en  ~470MB  balanced, ~5-7% WER  (default)
#   medium.en ~1.5GB  best English accuracy, ~4-6% WER
#   large-v3  ~3.1GB  multilingual
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# SIDEKICK_WHISPER_MODEL=small.en
# SIDEKICK_WHISPER_COMPUTE=int8
